api report sharp fall in drill estim oil and ga drill complet in the unit state drop by almost 41 per cent in 1986 from 1985 , the american petroleum institut said . api , an industri group , said that of the 42,387 well complet last year , a total of 19,741 were oil well , 8,645 were natur ga well and 14,001 were dri hole . in 1985 , a total of 71,539 well were drill - 36,834 oil well , 13,036 ga well and 21,669 dri hole .